    <h2>About</h2>
    <div class="card px-3 pt-3">
        <p><a href="https://phds.io">PhDs.io</a> is a platform created to support research students and academics as they navigate the vast and sometimes overwhelming body of literature in the fields of finance, accounting, and related areas. Our goal is simple: <strong>to make high-quality research more accessible and easier to explore</strong>.</p>

        <p>This project is developed by Dr. <a href="https://mingze-gao.com">Mingze Gao</a> from the Department of Applied Finance at Macquarie Business School, initiated when he was a postdoctoral research fellow at the University of Sydney Business School.

        <p>At PhDs.io, we have committed ourselves to carefully collecting, cleaning, and organizing references from reputable sources. We aim to provide a streamlined experience for users who are looking to deepen their knowledge, explore new areas of research, or simply stay up to date with the latest advancements.</p>

        <p>Whether you're a PhD student at the beginning of your academic journey or an established scholar, we hope you find this site to be a helpful companion. The path of research can be challenging, and weâ€™re here to offer a bit of support along the way.</p>

        <p><a href="https://mingze-gao.com/posts/phds.io/">Read more about PhDs.io here in my blog post.</a></p>
    </div>

